title: Eye Correction Cream-Gel
description:
DESCRIPTION: 
 
Contains vitamins, moisturizers and peptides intended for use around the eyes to moisturize the skin and diminish the appearance of wrinkles, eyebags and dark circles within 30 days of continued use. 
 
  
 
  
 
FORMS, DOSAGE & ADMINISTRATION: 
 
In Cream-Gel form.  For external  use only. Apply a small amount on the tip of the finger and move in a small gentle circular motion over, under and around the eye area until the product is absorbed.  Apply 0.5 cm away from the eye rim to avoid eye irritation. 
 
A Product of the Phils., formulated by a dermatologist. 
 
Distributed by:  NBR Medical Group, Inc

title: Moisturizing Cream
description:
DESCRIPTION:   
 
Contains glycerine, urea, HA and vitamins which increase ceramide and free fatty acid levels in the skin, prevents the skin from losing water content and stimulates micro-circulation in the skin.  Vitamins also keep the skin hydrated by preventing water loss and promote mild shedding of the skin that prevents pore blockage. 
 
  
 
FORM ,DOSAGE & ADMINISTRATION: 
 
In cream form.  For external use only. Gently apply on the face and neck. 
 
A Product of the Phils., formulated by a dermatologist. 
 
Distributed by:  NBR Medical Group, Inc.

title: Pimple Free Cream-Gel
description:
DESCRIPTION: 
 
Contains vitamins and keratolytics which help unclog pores and aid in clearing pimples in 2 to 4 weeks.   .   It assists the skin throughout the healing process by soothing and decreasing inflammation, irritation, peeling and swelling.  It sheds the stratum corneum decreasing the formation of comedones. 
 
  
 
  
 
FORM, DOSAGE & ADMINISTRATION: 
 
In cream-gel form.  For external use only.  Apply product to those areas of the face or body which have acne and comedones (black heads and white heads). 
 
A Product of the Phils., formulated by a dermatologist. 
 
Distributed by:  NBR Medical Group, Inc.

title: Collagen E Cream
description:
DESCRIPTION: 
 
Contains hydrolyzed collagen, amino acids, moisturizers and vitamins which help  shield skin cells from damage caused by free radicals.   It aids in cell repair preventing discoloration and scar caused by pimples and helps in the prevention of stretch marks, fine lines, wrinkles and sun/age spots. 
 
FORM, DOSAGE & ADMINISTRATION: 
 
In Cream Form.  For external use only.  Apply on face and neck daily at bedtime. 
 
A Product of the Phils., formulated by a dermatologist. 
 
Distributed by:  NBR Medical Group, Inc.

title: Replenishing Cream
description:
DESCRIPTION: 
 
Contains peptides,  vitamins,  moisturizers and antioxidants,  which help in the prevention of cell destruction and promote cell renewal to naturally replenish one’s skin 
 
FORM, DOSAGE & ADMINISTRATION: 
 
  
 
Comes in cream for external use only.   Apply on face and neck every night. 
 
A Product of the Phils., formulated by a dermatologist. 
 
Distributed by:  NBR Medical Group, Inc.
